text: Charlie Macleod (Charles MacLeod) is an English cricketer. He is a right- handed batsman and a wicketkeeper. He made his first-class debut for Leeds/Bradford MCC University against Yorkshire on 5 April 2013. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1992 births Category:Living people Category:English cricketers Category:Leeds/Bradford MCCU cricketers
